Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father says he's coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Is it that time of year already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! You've sure been cold-hearted lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you need to stay home this Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to... protect the banner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttering Banner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nobody suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep constantly on guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a team hunter around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A team hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Shinobu, your team, Blue Monday, \Nhailed from near Komatsu, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People from an unknown team \Nsuddenly approached our gathering spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us to choose: either \Nsubmit to them, or fight with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lost the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd... burn the team banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not unusual for us \Nto get challengers, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...that opponent was really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and our leader was no match for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I thought I should \Nat least protect our banner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so I took it and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You had it rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Their sleeves had that design on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... you're sure good at drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You never noticed before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd never seen that design before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Other teams are also talking about \Nthere having been a team hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the hunted teams \Ndid get their banner taken and burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're talking about having a meeting of \Nteam leaders to discuss countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your punk info network?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard it from an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this weekend, Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd better go to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An "old friend," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From once upon a time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Once upon a time," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't have the electricity \Nturned on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I forced my way in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody's welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And with Bro here, we'll be \Njust fine against some team hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worried about your teammates, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at this. It's our team banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We were proud of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We put our all into coming up with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and on the weekends, of course we met up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji seems strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? He's crazy strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he's not fighting lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... you're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If our leader had been strong, too, \Nthis wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd been strong enough to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, wanna stay here until things calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, anybody's welcome here. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My first time here, it was also like \NI'd shown up out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I think it's fine for you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, you two are \Nkinda like a big sister and big brother. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... for being a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi, Yu-yu, promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something to protect Blackout's banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to go through \Nwhat I'm going through right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to hide the banner someplace safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari said she hid it in \Nthe fishing-pond shed, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my father's coming home this weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving on minor business \Nfor two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Oh, what about the meeting of leaders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I’d better tell the others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll leave the rest in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I'll be away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You planning to work on a fishing boat \Nto earn a huge load of cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You could ride a fishing boat, or even a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! You can leave the rest to us! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If the team hunters show up, \Nwe'll drive them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget souvenirs, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better bring souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd better buy enough for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father says he's at the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What, already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I wear? \NWhich one do you think is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they both look nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Today \N Has Danji... come back yet...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Today \N Y: Has Danji... come back yet...? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet ;;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And today's the meeting of leaders! >_<
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This number cannot be reached at this t--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?\NThis number cannot be reached at this t--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's turned into fish food...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say something that'll tempt fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that was still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On urgent business. Got a problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also famous, and you have Zakusa along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea there were \Nthis many teams besides Blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply don't usually associate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The great thing about Vanguard is that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,people from any walk of life \Ncan fight in the same arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Blackout just send over their underlings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's treating this with quite a lot of contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Unlike you, our leader is very busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, chill out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gathered you all here for one reason:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To discuss what to do about \Nthose jokers doing this team hunt stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to have fun playing, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, it's a real nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashura 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your challengers can do \Nwhatever you like about winning or losing.\NAshura 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However...\NAshura 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not allow any banner burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our banner is a piece of team history and pride, \Npassed down by the members who came before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The act of burning a banner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...crosses a line that should never be crossed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu, have you changed in some way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's made a slightly offbeat friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! One a bit rough around the edges, \Nbut pretty good-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about those banner burners?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid who ran to us last week with a banner \Nsaw the custom sleeves they used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the design that was on their sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was this kid who ran to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He was from a team called Blue Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say, "Blue Monday"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They were wiped out two weeks ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And their banner got taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How would he have that banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that kid must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better rush back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did everybody go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are these scattered around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was by the merry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They... they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "they"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu! Thank goodness you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Masanori, they're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's "Mister" Masanori to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Masanori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This prank you're playing isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The funny part starts now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we don't need this anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Blue Monday's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,About time we get to burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the ones who've been \Ngoing around burning team banners?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I dunno, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a new banner, in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it right where you said it was, big sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi, you're so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is your goal here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, where's Yu-yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, he's not coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done playing, Masanori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya Ebata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Masanori, quit the silly pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Win first, then take the banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now... we've got the scene all laid out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want the banner to burn, fight us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose, we'll take custody of the banner,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll activate this switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! But what will activating that switch do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to look forward to finding that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... let me play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll leave Megumi to you, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a revenge match with Zakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn! I ride Charis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu won against you, so I can, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take another win against you this time, \Nusing the full power of my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in good spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just fine, step on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it hotter than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a straightforward way of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I'm not gonna forgive you so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I misjudged you, you unfair jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm unfair? Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you fools a lesson \Nfor your peace-loving complacency. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Bastion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I call four units.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, with Dark Strain's skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,grade 3s gain the Boost ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Phanuel attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates: an extra critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to realize that this is a battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion's skill activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a grade 3 was triggered, I restand Phanuel! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it gets +10,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,World Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Abyssal Dark Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Great play, there. I’ve got chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack your Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll do no guard against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my calculations aren't panning out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd better work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alchemagic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do Vanguard all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the dark, dark abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your opponent chooses where you end up going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Orfist attacks your Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so unfriendly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...however...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...you've already begun sinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper, and deeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitz Order! I play Sealed Path!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My opponent's Vanguard gets -1 critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a huge mistake by assuming \Nthat the darkness was entirely on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also evildoers \Nwho prefer to dwell in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for you... for the likes of \Nyou guys... stealing it away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't protect it... \Nthen there's no coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First check!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Front trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Second check!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling during a fight reveals too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't protect anything \Nwith that level of preparedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alchemagic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alchemagic again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of two people sinking into darkness, \Nthe one approaching closer to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be swallowed by fear before drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona Ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a bad fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While the darkness may feel welcoming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should take better care next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. It's really not that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you've made some good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't today when you go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I do that every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was around your age, \Nfriends felt more important than family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you'd rather go... \NI mean, you should just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy-peasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've done more to be certain \Nthat you'd finish me off on your previous turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a paltry attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.41,0:23:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of naively assuming \Nthat there'd be a next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, Danji... just what are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...at such a crucial time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time for this one's turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna activate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tell me! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it gonna do?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.30,0:25:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.88,0:25:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Masanori.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.17,0:26:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce my card: \N Mysterious Rain Spiritualist, Zorga!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.19,0:26:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorga is a genius at handling the Drop Zone. \NIt can resurrect any unit from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.86,0:26:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course this goes beyond regular units: \NOrder cards are also Zorga's playthings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.79,0:26:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After playing a Normal Order,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.55,0:26:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,by using Alchemagic on \Nan Order card in the Drop Zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.27,0:26:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go on to produce its effect, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.03,0:26:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It basically makes the Drop Zone a second hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.41,0:26:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.17,0:26:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.18,0:26:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Dragon's Ceremony 
